      "text": "These kind spirits were two childlike spirits who inhabited the Spirit Wilds and frequented its oasis. They were among the first spirits to befriend Wan after he had been banished from his lion turtle city."
    },
    {
      "body": "The two kind spirits were entering the spirit oasis, when Wan was caught sneaking in by the ${link_0}. After he explained his banishment from the fire lion turtle city, the two spirits expressed pity for him and suggested he search for another lion turtle city. They wished him luck as he left to find another human civilization.",
