      ],
      "text": "The two kind spirits were entering the spirit oasis, when Wan was caught sneaking in by the aye-aye spirit. After he explained his banishment from the fire lion turtle city, the two spirits expressed pity for him and suggested he search for another lion turtle city. They wished him luck as he left to find another human civilization."
    },
    {
      "body": "The kind spirits were delighted to learn that ${link_0} had decided he had had enough of humanity, deciding to live among the spirits and learn their ways.",
